Aggregation.Name: Aggregate
Aggregation.SQLExpression:
"N$10117" as (SELECT t0."ACCOUNTID", t0."AMOUNTCREDIT_AVG", t0."AMOUNTDEBIT_AVG", t0."ACCOUNTID_COUNT" FROM (SELECT "ACCOUNTID", AVG("AMOUNTCREDIT") "AMOUNTCREDIT_AVG" ,AVG("AMOUNTDEBIT") "AMOUNTDEBIT_AVG" ,COUNT("ACCOUNTID") "ACCOUNTID_COUNT" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE}
GROUP BY "ACCOUNTID") t0 )

Transformation.Name: Transform 1
Transformation.SQLExpression: "N$10031" AS ( SELECT "CUSTOMERCODE", "CLOSED", "DATEOFDORMANCY", "LASTCREDITTRANSDTTM", "DEBITBASECODE", "STATUS", "DORMANTSTATUS", "OPENEDBYTELLER", "PRODUCT", "BRANCHCODE", "ACCOUNTID", "CLOSUREDATE", "UBMODEOFOPERATION", "ENROLLMENTCODE", "DEBITLIMIT", "RECLASTMODIFIEDDATE", "CURRENCY", "LASTTRANSACTIONDATE", "LOWESTBALANCE", "CREDITBASECODE", "CREDITLIMIT", "DORMANTDATE", "LOANPRINCIPALAMOUNT", "INTERESTSTARTDATE", "LOWESTBALANCEDATE", "SEGMENTATION", "LASTDEBITTRANSDTTM", "DATEOPENED",CASE PRODUCT WHEN '21051' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as "SMART" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )

TransformationElementType.CustomTransformationEx: CASE PRODUCT WHEN '21051' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END

Transformation.Name: Transform 2
Transformation.SQLExpression: "N$10158" AS ( SELECT "CUSTOMERCODE", "SHORTNAME", "FIRSTNAME", "UBRELATIONSHIPMGRID", "SUBCATEGORY", "CUSTOMERTYPE", "KYCSTATUS", "NRCNO", "CUSTOMERSUBTYPE", "LASTNAME", "DATEMODIFIED", "DOB", "SEGMENTATION", "GENDER", "ADDRESSLINE3", "ADDRESSLINE2", "ADDRESSLINE5", "ADDRESSLINE4", "BLACKLISTED", "DATECREATED",ROUND((2018 - TO_NUMBER(SUBSTR(DOB, 1, 4))), -1) as "DOB_AGE",CASE WHEN gender is null THEN 'Unknown' WHEN gender = 'Male' THEN 'Male' WHEN gender = 'Female' THEN 'Female' ELSE 'Unknown' END as "GENDER_MOD" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )

TransformationElementType.CustomTransformationEx: CASE WHEN gender is null THEN 'Unknown' WHEN gender = 'Male' THEN 'Male' WHEN gender = 'Female' THEN 'Female' ELSE 'Unknown' END
